OL,6,FA drink-driver who crashed into a tree
OL,7,Fat high speed, killing his passenger,
OL,8,Fafter a night out, has been sentenced
OL,9,Fto seven years in a young offenders
OL,10,Finstitute.
OL,12,FCanterbury Crown Court heard that 18-
OL,13,Fyear-old Ethan Entwistle, the front
OL,14,Fseat passenger, was killed instantly
OL,15,Fby the impact.
