OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,FColby Hammond, was also 18 at the
OL,7,Ftime, was behind the wheel of the Seat
OL,8,FIbiza and had been drinking alcohol
OL,9,Fwith Ethan and two other friends at
OL,10,Fvarious bars across Broadstairs and
OL,11,Fthen Ramsgate until 3am.
OL,13,FHammond was twice the drink-drive
OL,14,Flimit, then when driving them home
OL,15,Fafterwards, he drove the wrong way
OL,16,Fdown a one-way street.
OL,18,FHe travelled along Dumpton Park Drive,
OL,19,Fgreatly in excess of the 30mph speed
OL,20,Flimit. He crashed at 70 mph in
OL,21,FBroadstairs on Sunday 1 October 2023.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
