OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,FThe court heard how Hammond ignored
OL,7,Fthe plea of Ethan and others in the
OL,8,Fcar to slow down.
OL,10,FHammond had pleaded guilty at an
OL,11,Fearlier hearing.
OL,13,FEthan's mum has been campaigning for
OL,14,Fyoung drivers under the age of 21 to
OL,15,Fhave restrictions imposed for six
OL,16,Fmonths after passing their test, it
OL,17,Fwould be known as Graduated Driver
OL,18,FLicensing
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/8
