OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,FKeena Entwistle said: "Ethan could
OL,7,Fstill be here. What we're asking for
OL,8,Fis only six months for young drivers
OL,9,Faged under 21, after passing their
OL,10,Ftest that they don't have peer aged
OL,11,Fpassengers in the car with them unless
OL,12,Fthey have someone over the age of 25.
OL,14,F"Obviously there would be exemptions
OL,15,Fif they've got young children
OL,16,Fthemselves, or it's an emergency,
OL,17,Fthings like that.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/8
