OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,F"We're saying that between certain
OL,7,Fhours from 12 at night to 6 in the
OL,8,Fmorning they're not to use the car,
OL,9,Fagain unless there are exceptions."
OL,11,FThe campaign has the backing of the
OL,12,FAssociation of Police and Crime
OL,13,FCommissioners.
OL,15,FHammond, of Westwood Road,
OL,16,FBroadstairs, admitted to attending
OL,17,Fofficers that he had been drinking
OL,18,Fthat night and was subsequently
OL,19,Fcharged with causing death by
OL,20,Fdangerous driving.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/8
