OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,FHe pleaded guilty to the offence at
OL,7,FCanterbury Crown Court, and on
OL,8,FThursday 28 August 2025, Hammond, now
OL,9,F20, was sentenced to seven years in
OL,10,Fprison.
OL,12,FHe will also be banned for driving for
OL,13,Fsix years and must take an extended
OL,14,Fretest before he is allowed to drive
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,17,FJudge Simon James told Hammond: "Ethan
OL,18,Fwas a vibrant and popular young man, a
OL,19,Fbeloved son, brother and friend to so
OL,20,Fmany.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/8
