OL,3,CDrink-driver who crashed into tree on
OL,4,Cnight out killing passenger, sentenced
OL,6,F"There is no sentence I can impose
OL,7,Fthat can come anywhere near to
OL,8,Fbringing peace and solace to his
OL,9,Ffamily friends."
OL,11,FInvestigating officer DC Lee Berridge
OL,12,Fsaid: "Holding a driving licence is
OL,13,Fone of great responsibility.
OL,15,F"When you pass, you owe it to
OL,16,Fyourself, the wider public and
OL,17,Fcertainly those within your car that
OL,18,Fentrust you as a driver, to get them
OL,19,Fto your destination safely.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
